properties.areaDesc: Coastal Waters from Pigeon Point to Point Pinos California out to 10 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 7 at 2:49AM PST until February 8 at 9:00PM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt
expected.

* WHERE...Coastal Waters from Pigeon Point to Point Pinos
California out to 10 nm.

* WHEN...From 9 AM to 9 PM PST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM TO 9 PM PST SATURDAY
